## Notes
- The `ubuntu` username is correct for DLAMI Ubuntu 22.04 — do not use `ec2-user`
- All trials use `WANDB_RUN_GROUP=<sweep_name>` so they are grouped in the W&B dashboard
- If a trial fails, the runner script continues to the next trial (set -e is per-trial, not per-script)
- Spot instances may be interrupted — if an instance dies mid-sweep, report which trials were lost and offer to re-run them
- For `env` hyperparam_mode, convert param names to UPPER_CASE (e.g. `learning_rate` → `LEARNING_RATE`)
- Cost estimate: check spot price with `aws ec2 describe-spot-price-history --instance-types <type> --product-descriptions "Linux/UNIX" --region us-east-2 --query 'SpotPriceHistory[0].SpotPrice'`
